om.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2020-02-18 01:35:08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，2月15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">郭文貴死期：2020 年 6 月 4 日</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n放心你就快唔會再睇到佢出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f7967c3230d2053d253799ba185f7adbffbdc3","tid":1923060,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac4528f016f3723e711fec110f832879cd51a3f","tid":1923060,"uid":115700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"係人都知<br />\n差在今年定出年"},{"pid":"bb7d35f0a134f8cd442f2b74dd68456c46b4b17c","tid":1923060,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac4528f016f3723e711fec110f832879cd51a3f","tid":1923060,"uid":115700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"係人都知<br />\n差在今年定出年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"你幾時知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336b6d1315d4dbd535b9c43add422b71211dc351","tid":1923060,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/l